column2: "So is this the guy the other Dragonkin was talking about?"
"〔This past〕〔Conversation〕〔If you understand〕〔Our words〕〔Our meaning〕〔Then go〕"
"He sure knows how to pique my interest. Let's see what's waiting ahead."
"We should still be careful. There's a chance it might be a trap."
"You know, you can leave anytime. Your fear of heights, freaking out all the time... I can't believe you're in the ARKS."
